Chili

2 tbsp olive oil
1 lb. ground turkey (or beef)
1 tbsp. minced garlic
1-2 chopped onions
1/2 chopped green pepper
1 lg can cut tomatoes
1 lg can kidney beans (sometimes I also add a can of corn)
1 sm can tomato sauce
2-4 squares dark chocolate (75-85%)
1 tbsp chili powder
2 tsp cumin
a dozen or so shakes of tabasco sauce (or green tabasco sauce)
salt, pepper to taste

Heat the oil and brown meat, onions, garlic and green pepper.  Add
canned ingredients and all seasonings and simmer 15-20 minutes.
